{"ts":"2026-06-23T19:52:28.062Z","author":"claude-code-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-cn0c"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"composeExtensionPackage: author-once capstone returning { module, manifest }"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Add composeExtensionPackage(blueprint, identity): ExtensionPackage to src/sdk/compose.ts — the author-once capstone that unifies composeExtension + synthesizeExtensionManifest. Synthesize the complete least-privilege manifest from the blueprint + identity, then compose the ExtensionModule with that synthesized manifest set as its authoritative in-module mirror, so the runtime module and the on-disk manifest.json are generated from one source and can never drift. Returns { module, manifest }: write module as the package entry default export, write manifest as manifest.json. Pure assembler (no validation/loading); pairs with preflightExtension for the verify step. Completes the declarative loop end-to-end: author (define*) -> assemble modularly (merge) -> ship both halves (composeExtensionPackage)."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Task"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["area:extensions","area:sdk","authoring","dx"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-06-23T19:52:28.062Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-23T19:52:28.062Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"claude-code-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-2p38"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"8b42425a4957e64557e477d3d61fe8b0d63d125e8a9c07a94136d948519559b8","message":""}
